<P>

<DT> <I><B>Invasion from Aldebaran (Inwazja z Aldebarana)</B></I>, 1959.
<DD> Collection of SF-short stories.
<P>
<DL>
	<DD> Do you exist, Mr. Johnes?
	<DD> Friend.
	<DD> Test.
	<DD> Albatross.
	<DD> The Invasion from Aldebaran.
	<DD> Darkness and Mildes.
	<DD> Hammer.
	<DD> Invasion.
	<DD> Exodus.
</DL>
<P>

``Test'' and ``Albatross'' belong to the Pirx stories.  (Thank you to
